{"type":"message","id":"419719df","parentId":"01d5966f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:01:49.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've been having issues with tool calls being malformed. The sessionStatus tool is expecting a valid model parameter. Let me try without the model parameter and correctly call session_status.\n\nLooking at the history of this conversation, I realize that my tool calls have been getting corrupted somehow - the function name and parameters are being merged incorrectly.\n\nLet me just provide a response to the user directly since I've already identified the issue from reading the file. ","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"   现在我发现问题了。这不是内容类型的问题，而是**处理流程的缺陷**：\n\n## 🔍 问题分析\n\n我查看了这篇文章的 HTML 源码，发现：\n\n1. **词汇表完全为空** - `<tbody></tbody>` 没有任何内容\n2. **正文中没有任何 `word-block` 标注** - 全是纯文本 `<p>` 标签\n3. **底部有来源声明** - 说明是从微信公众号「笔记侠」转载的\n\n## 🎯 根本原因\n\n对比 MEMORY.md 中的内容规范：\n- 正常文章应该对重点英文词汇标注 `<span class=\"word-block\">...</span>`\n- 词汇表应该与正文标注一一对应\n\n**但这篇文章的问题在于：**\n- 原文是纯中文古诗词赏析，没有英文原稿可参照\n- 处理流程**没有正确处理无外文来源的文章**\n- 系统没有为这类纯中文内容**主动选择适合标注的词汇**\n\n## 🛠️ 修复方案\n\n两种选择：\n\n**A. 手动补充词汇**（推荐）\n我可以为这篇文章手动添加恰当的英文标注，比如：\n- 文学术语（poem, Zen, enlightenment）\n- 概念词汇（philosophy, adversity, transcendence）\n- 人名地名（Su Shi, Donglin Temple, Huangzhou）\n\n**B. 修改处理流程**\n在 `scripts/` 中添加一个检查：如果一篇文章生成后词汇表为空，应该：\n1. 触发二次词汇选择\n2. 或为纯中文文章使用不同的词汇提取策略\n\n---\n\n你希望我怎么处理？是手动修复这篇文章，还是优化整个处理流程？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":88,"output":545,"cacheRead":71552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775278879604}}
