{"type":"message","id":"fef15871","parentId":"c45475c4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T11:40:51.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"明白了，用户想让我分析 MinoX 工程，找出可以优化的地方。让我读取工程文件，了解项目结构和代码。\n\n我需要读取：\n1. 项目的 README.md（已经在之前的对话中读取了）\n2. workflow/mingox.py - 主流程脚本\n3. util/annotate_lib.py - 标注库\n4. 一些 posts/ 下的示例文章\n5. content/drafts/README.md - 草稿目录说明\n6. docs/PIPELINE.md - 流程说明\n\n让我开始读取这些文件。 ","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"   好的，让我深入分析这个工程。我会先读取关键文件了解整体架构。  "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":":workflow/mingox.py"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/docs/PIPELINE.md"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":",workflow/mingox.py"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:3","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"./workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/workflow/mingox.py"}},{"type":"text","text":" "}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":630,"output":366,"cacheRead":88288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775302843452}}
